05:37.850 --> 05:42.850
== sync, corrected by <font color="#00FF00">elderman</font> ==

05:42.875 --> 05:51.200
♪

05:58.138 --> 06:00.606
Why can't we just get him to a cab,
take him to the hospital ourselves?

06:00.734 --> 06:02.016
No, we can't move him.

06:02.018 --> 06:03.268
Mom!
Look,

06:03.270 --> 06:05.052
I don't know what's wrong with
him; it might be his neck.

06:05.054 --> 06:06.638
If we move him,
we could make it worse.

06:06.662 --> 06:08.662
I'm not going
to take that chance.

06:08.664 --> 06:10.265
JACK: Aunt Erin,
we need to do something.

06:11.261 --> 06:12.527
Excuse me.

06:12.529 --> 06:14.045
What do we got?

06:14.047 --> 06:14.962
It was a bike accident.

06:14.964 --> 06:17.115
He hit his head hard.

06:17.117 --> 06:18.566
He's been in and out
of consciousness.

06:18.568 --> 06:20.101
Okay, step back.
Okay.

06:28.110 --> 06:29.777
Is he going to be okay?

06:29.779 --> 06:32.113
Yeah, he's going
to be okay.

06:36.735 --> 06:39.570
One, two, three.

